<br>
A level 53 Mage is almost completely ineffective against the new mobs on the upper floors in terms of casting, the failure rate was 90% when it was not malo'd and 50% when it was Malo'd. I tried all the tools available and had varying success.<br>
<br>
Shock of Swords: 1 in 32 stuck for full<br>
Elemental Maelstorm: Never stuck except with Malo<br>
Char: Best success but still nothing to write home to Jababer about<br>
Lava Bolt: Cannot remember for sure but I had one stick in several hours and the mob summoned and killed me.<br>
<br>
